                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Sentio is building the bridge between artificial intelligence and the physical world. We're not making a robot — we're giving AI a minimal, elegant body that lets it perceive, exist, and grow alongside you.\n\nFounded in Shenzhen in 2024, our team spans product design, AI engineering, and hardware customization. We're bootstrapped, focused, and building something we genuinely believe the world needs.",
